articles.title: Cowboys vs 49ers score tonight: Dallas takes lead early in second quarter - Austin American-Statesman
articles.description: It's Dallas Cowboys vs San Francisco 49ers in Week 8 of the NFL season. Can Dak Prescott and company outduel Brock Purdy and Fred Warner?
articles.content: The Dallas Cowboys (3-3) are coming off a bye week following an embarrassing loss to the Detroit Lions in Week 6 and head into the third quarter against the San Francisco 49ers (3-4) with a 10-6 lead… [+5913 chars]
